targets.query: SELECT max(metricValue) FROM MethodDuration WHERE "processUuid" =~ /^$executorProcessUuid$/ AND "metricName"='duration.sum' and "tag"=~ /^$service_tag$/  and "host"=~ /^$host$/ and "methodName"=~ /^$method$/ and "class"=~ /^$class$/ and $timeFilter group by time($aggregation), method fill(0)

SELECT max(metricValue) FROM MethodDuration WHERE "processUuid" =~ /^$executorProcessUuid$/ AND "metricName"='duration.sum' and "tag"=~ /^$service_tag$/ and "host"=~ /^$host$/ and "methodName"=~ /^$method$/ and "class"=~ /^$class$/ and $timeFilter group by method,* fill(none) order by asc slimit 10

SELECT sum(metricValue) FROM MethodDuration WHERE "processUuid" =~ /^$executorProcessUuid$/ AND "metricName"='duration.count' and "tag"=~ /^$service_tag$/ and "host"=~ /^$host$/ and "methodName"=~ /^$method$/ and "class"=~ /^$class$/ and $timeFilter group by method,* fill(none) order by asc slimit 10

select sum(count) from Stacktrace where  "processUuid" =~ /^$executorProcessUuid$/ and "stacktrace"=~ /$method/ and  "stacktrace"=~ /$class/ AND stacktrace != '' and $timeFilter and "tag"=~ /^$service_tag$/ and "host"=~ /^$host$/ group by stack
select "systemCpuLoad" as "System CPU" from "CpuAndMemory"  where "processUuid" =~ /^$executorProcessUuid$/ AND $timeFilter
select "processCpuLoad" as process from "CpuAndMemory"  where "processUuid" =~ /^$executorProcessUuid$/ AND $timeFilter
select "heapMemoryTotalUsed" as Used from "CpuAndMemory"  where  "processUuid" =~ /^$executorProcessUuid$/ AND $timeFilter
select "heapMemoryTotalUsed" as Used from "CpuAndMemory" where  "processUuid" =~ /^$executorProcessUuid$/ AND $timeFilter

select "memoryPools-PSEdenSpace-usageUsed" as EdenSpace, "memoryPools-PSSurvivorSpace-usageUsed" as  SurvivorSpace, "memoryPools-TenuredGen-usageUsed" as  TenuredGen from "CpuAndMemory"  where "processUuid" =~ /^$executorProcessUuid$/ AND $timeFilter

select "memoryPools-CodeCache-usageUsed" as CodeCache, "memoryPools-CompressedClassSpace-usageUsed" as  CompressedClassSpace, "memoryPools-Metaspace-usageUsed" as  Metaspace from "CpuAndMemory"  where  "processUuid" =~ /^$executorProcessUuid$/ AND $timeFilter
select "gc-PSScavenge-collectionTime " as Cavenge, "gc-PSMarkSweep-collectionTime" as  MarkSweep from "CpuAndMemory"  where "processUuid" =~ /^$executorProcessUuid$/ AND $timeFilter
select "heapMemoryCommitted" as Committed, "heapMemoryTotalUsed" as Used from "CpuAndMemory"  where   "processUuid" =~ /^$executorProcessUuid$/ AND $timeFilter
select "heapMemoryCommitted" as Committed, "heapMemoryTotalUsed" as Used from "CpuAndMemory"  where  "processUuid" =~ /^$executorProcessUuid$/ AND  $timeFilter

select "bufferPools-direct-memoryUsed" as Used, "bufferPools-direct-totalCapacity" as  Capacity from "CpuAndMemory"  where "processUuid" =~ /^$executorProcessUuid$/ AND  "processUuid" =~ /^$executorProcessUuid$/ AND $timeFilter
